_sText:
gg_fatal_cache is a tightly packed, balanced, semi-symmetrical fight yard style gungame map for fast-paced, close-quarters combat within a destructible warehouse environment.

Buy zones, 3D skybox, lots of destructibles and a large 2D skybox height.

Navigation file, installation tutorial and load screen text file are all included within download. Thanks and PLEASE LEAVE A REVIEW.
